    {
      "bookmarkId": "22486240_18_988-1088",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "988-1088",
      "markText": "动物之间的很多不友好和好斗的行为都是在群体中缺乏安全感的表现。你面前的动物一定要知道它的位置在哪里，是在你之上还是在你之下。动物在群体中的地位对它如何生活至关重要。地位决定了它可以与谁交往，如何交往；",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22486240&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=988&rangeEnd=1088",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffd328c071571ce0ffd2bbf?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=988&rangeEnd=1088"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22486240_40_1185-1239",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "1185-1239",
      "markText": "事情并没有像我们预想的那样发生，你能怎么办呢？无论生活以怎样的方式向你走来，你都必须接受它，尽可能地享受它。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22486240&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1239",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffd328c071571ce0ffd2bbf?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1239"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22486240_6_2418-2460",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2418-2460",
      "markText": "当你在生活中经历了很多痛苦折磨之后，每一次新的痛苦都既令人无法忍受又让人感到微不足道",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22486240&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2418&rangeEnd=2460",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffd328c071571ce0ffd2bbf?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2418&rangeEnd=2460"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22486240_6_1577-1628",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1577-1628",
      "markText": "就靠行动迟缓而生存。它总是睡意蒙眬，懒懒散散，这使它远离伤害，躲开美洲豹、豹猫、热带大雕和森蚺的注意。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22486240&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1577&rangeEnd=1628",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffd328c071571ce0ffd2bbf?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1577&rangeEnd=1628"
    },
    {
