      "chapterUid": 90,
      "range": "741-788",
      "markText": "闪电对我的影响却截然相反。它把我从有限的平凡之中拉了出来，猛地将我推进了兴奋和惊奇的状态之中。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22486240&chapterUid=90&rangeStart=741&rangeEnd=788",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffd328c071571ce0ffd2bbf?chapterUid=90&rangeStart=741&rangeEnd=788"
